=head1 Procedure

  Part B: All-Nodes Multicast Destination
   6. Repeat Steps 1 through 5 from Part A. Router Solicitation A has a Destination Address of the
      All-Nodes multicast address.

=head1 Observable Results

  Parts A-C
   In all Parts, the HUT should send a multicast Neighbor Solicitation for TN1 in Step 5,
   indicating the HUT did not process the Router Solicitation from TN1.

